    G --> H[Log issues & findings in draft.md]
    H --> I[Update dependency graph]
    I --> F
    F -- No more files --> J[Compare draft.md with target_functionality.md]
    J --> K[Write final_report.md]
    K --> L[Generate action_plan.md]
    L --> M[âœ… Done]
```

